title: For Sale:  BRAND NEW Kel-Tec PMR-30 black
postcontent: FOR SALE:  BRAND NEW Kel-Tec PMR-30 .22WMR full-size pistol.  2 magazines.  Never been fired.  Color:  black.  Magazine capacity:  30.  Weight unloaded:  14 oz.  Overall length:  7.9".  Barrel length:  4.3".  Height:  5.8".  Width:  1.3".  Trigger pull:  5 lbs.  "With a unique hybrid blow-back system that takes a .22 magnum (.22WMR), 30 round magazine, this 13.6 ounce, full-size pistol is one heavy duty performer.  Its innovative operation system also allows for the use of a wide variety of ammunition.  With its light, crisp trigger pull and fiber optic sights, the PMR-30 is ideal for target shooting and hunting small game."I bought two brand new Kel-Tec PMR-30s at the same time.  My intention was to get my CCDW and use one on my hip and one on my ankle.  It's too big for my ankle, so I'm selling one.  I've only used one of these guns and kept the other one brand new in the box.  I absolutely love this gun!  There's no recoil, it's fun and easy to use, and it holds 30 rounds.  I'm using it for target practice and self-defense at home.  I seriously doubt that any intruder has 30 rounds to work with, so I feel confident with 30 rounds that I can fend off an intruder until the police arrive if need be.  This gun is perfect for anyone, particularly if you don't like the recoil that most guns have, and if you're new to shooting, it's a terrific choice for learning the basic skills of hitting a target.  This gun is really hard to find, and most gun stores sell out fast when they do get one.  Ask any gun dealer.  They'll tell you the same thing.  Most dealers have no idea when their next shipment of them will arrive either.  It's frustrating trying to find one, especially in black.  At least that was my experience.
